{"tid":1986591,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"口交部：根本不存在野生動物濕貨市場","createTime":"2020-04-24T02:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T03:55:36.000Z","uid":159697,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d37095230bf09c435a4df13c7de24c1580dc59ef","tid":1986591,"uid":159697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國國務卿蓬佩奧再次批評中國，未有在新冠病毒疫情爆發初期及時向世界衛生組織通報，並且隱瞞病毒出現人傳人；又指中國利用今次疫情挑釁打壓周邊地區。在北京，外交部指摘美方顛倒黑白、挑撥離間。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧繼續質疑中國處理新型冠狀病毒疫情的手法，指華府堅信中方沒有及時向世衛通報爆發疫情。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧同時指摘中國藉全球忙於應對疫情之際，持續作出挑釁行為，包括繼續蠶食香港的自治、拘捕民主黨創黨主席李柱銘等民主派人士、對台灣施加軍事壓力及脅迫南海周邊國家。他重申華府強烈反對有關霸凌行為，希望其他國家向北京追究責任。<br />\n<br />\n武漢早在去年年底已出現首批患者，華南海鮮市場更加被指是病毒傳播源頭，蓬佩奧指，基於這類濕街市非法售賣的野味與人畜共通傳染病有強烈關聯，美方已經呼籲中國永久關閉出售野味的濕街市。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部重申台灣和香港事務均屬中國內政，不容許外部勢力干涉。耿爽又指，中國根本不存在所謂的「野生動物濕貨市場」，並且已經立法全面禁止非法野生動物的捕獵、交易、運輸和食用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93f264350c1b6023e05dc4afae7d975874651cd","tid":1986591,"uid":159697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"華南海鮮批發市場：am I a joke to you?"},{"pid":"5b51b4f035384fa950276d1128ea22306362b6d0","tid":1986591,"uid":48286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a93f264350c1b6023e05dc4afae7d975874651cd","tid":1986591,"uid":159697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"華南海鮮批發市場：am I a joke to you?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"口交爽: 你啲野味人工飼養出嚟㗎"},{"pid":"b284c142bfa5fa626faa9e9253360745de9fb542","tid":1986591,"uid":36724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b51b4f035384fa950276d1128ea22306362b6d0","tid":1986591,"uid":48286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a93f264350c1b6023e05dc4afae7d975874651cd","tid":1986591,"uid":159697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"華南海鮮批發市場：am I a joke to you?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:55:09.000Z","msg":"口交爽: 你啲野味人工飼養出嚟㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"之前話禁止野味買賣<br />\n<br />\n都估到會重新譯法咩野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7630512ed0b0f9c4ed7cfc7eabbe67872ce4c113","tid":1986591,"uid":264892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:01:16.000Z","msg":"我諗佢口中嘅野味應該係青龍 白虎 朱雀 玄武 麒麟"},{"pid":"16bbeb1859c6d3de07dbcfe0022878d425588f28","tid":1986591,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:02:40.000Z","msg":"華南海鮮市場唔係一般所定義嘅野味市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f933367ec8ea46608c01c820e09d6adecb2d54e5","tid":1986591,"uid":160566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:04:08.000Z","msg":"沒有野生動物市場 只有p4實驗室<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf8953e4ce918a96d44403029af097cd3481c50","tid":1986591,"uid":39492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a93f264350c1b6023e05dc4afae7d975874651cd","tid":1986591,"uid":159697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"華南海鮮批發市場：am I a joke to you?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"冇「野生動物濕貨市場」, 不過有「武漢華南海鮮批發市場」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2318595605f8125f2e8cd058d55045c1db060e7","tid":1986591,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"因為係乾貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b21185a3f44fda7ada3d1655ffae7d3bc3d904f","tid":1986591,"uid"